Class AddPlantsView

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.View
pkgMain.AddPlantsView
Direct Known Subclasses:
AddPreexistingView, DesignGardenView
public class AddPlantsView
extends View
Class - AddPlantsView, this class contains methods that extend to other view scenes to display things on screen like icons and plant descriptions.
Author:
William Cantera, Diane Vinson, Ben Testani, Jacob Kuchma, Maria van Venrooy
